# 🔄 Spring vs Spring Boot

| Spring Framework         | Spring Boot        |
| ------------------------ | ------------------ |
| Requires Configuration   | Auto Configuration |
| External Server Required | Embedded Server    |
| XML Configuration        | Annotation Based   |
| Complex Setup            | Easy Setup         |
| Slower Development       | Faster Development |

